deck: As Robert Gonzalez makes his move, Coulson must do whatever it takes to protect the future of S.H.I.E.L.D. Meanwhile, Skye’s journey to control her powers takes a surprising turn when she meets the enigmatic Inhuman named Lincoln.
description: Following an incident where rogue S.H.I.E.L.D. agents made contact with Skye, Hunter and Coulson travel to the safe house, but Skye flees to a mountain retreat with the help of Gordon, an "Inhuman" like her.
name: Afterlife

deck: As Norman grows closer to Emma, he starts growing apart from Norma; Norma balks when Romero asks Norman some tough questions; and Romero meets his competition for reelections.
name: Persuasion

description:
Japanese title: Akamaru bikkuri! Gaara, Kyōi no Jitsuryoku (赤丸ビックリ!我愛羅, 驚異の実力)

The Sound ninja depart after witnessing Sasuke's intense power. Naruto's team finally gets a moment of peace to recuperate.
name: Akamaru Trembles: Gaara's Cruel Strength!

description:
Japanese title:Nozokimi genkin! Makimono no himitsu (のぞき見厳禁!巻き物の秘密)

To heal their wounds, Naruto and his team take a much-needed rest after their battle against the Sound ninja. But it has already been four days since the start of the exam and there is only one day remaining until time expires.
name: The Scroll's Secret: No Peeking Allowed

deck: Captain Cold and Heat Wave have returned!
description: Thawne warns Barry not to change any event for fear that he will create a bigger problem. Barry does not listen and instead captures Mardon and puts him in the particle accelerator. Snart and Rory return to Central City. Snart sends his sister, Lisa after Cisco, whom they force to rebuild the cold and heat guns, and a third gun shooting gold for Lisa, by threatening to kill Cisco's brother. Iris rejects Barry's romantic approach and later Eddie punches him. Barry realizes that Thawne was right about not to manipulate the timeline. Cisco returns and reveals that Snart forced him to reveal the Flash's true identity. Barry goes after Snart, and the two come to a truce: Snart will not reveal Barry's identity, will no longer kill innocent people, and stay away from Barry's loved ones in exchange for Barry not locking him away in the particle accelerator. Caitlin tells Eddie and Iris that Barry is suffering from psychosis as a result of the lightning, making the duo reconcile with him and settling the tension. The Reverse-Flash kills Mason and destroys the evidence linking Thawne to Stagg's death. Mason's vanishing causes Barry to accept Joe was right about "Wells".
name: Rogue Time

description: As the Powers divison races to stop Wolfe from escaping, flashbacks reveal Christian and Wolfe's past.
name: Paint it Black

description:
Japanese title: Bunshin taiketsu! Ore ga shuyaku dattebayo! (分身対決!オレが主役だってばよ!)

Naruto's team joins Kabuto on their journey to the tower, but on the way, they are trapped by the genjutsu (illusion technique) of the Hidden Rain Village's genin (low rank ninja), Oboro's team.
name: Clone Vs. Clone: Mine are Better than Yours!

description:
Japanese title: Daini shiken toppa! Seizoroi rūkī nain! (第二試験突破!勢ぞろいルーキーナイン!)

When Naruto and his team open the two scrolls after reaching the tower, Iruka suddenly appears.
name: Surviving the Cut! The Rookie Nine Together Again!

description:
Japanese title: Gōkakusha nibun ni ichi!? Ikinari shiai dattebayo!! (合格者二分の一!?イキナリ試合だってばよ!!)

The 21 ninjas that passed the second exam assemble for their next challenge.
name: Narrowing the Field: Sudden Death Elimination!

description:
Japanese title: Geji mayu jerashī! "Shishi Rendan" Tanjō (ゲジまゆジェラシー!「獅子連弾」誕生!)

The preliminaries for the third exam are one on one combat, and the first match is between Sasuke and Orochimaru's minion Yoroi.
name: Bushy Brow's Jealousy: Barrage of Lions Unleashed!

description:
Japanese title: Isshoku sokuhatsu!! Kakashi vāsasu Orochimaru (一触即発!!カカシVS大蛇丸)

As Kakashi safely releases Sasuke from the spell, Orochimaru suddenly shows up. Orochimaru expresses his desire for the power of Sharingan that the Uchiha clan holds in order to fulfill his ambitions.
name: Kakashi and Orochimaru: Face-to-Face!

description:
Japanese title: Raibaru gekitotsu! Otomegokoro wa honki mōdo (ライバル激突!オトメ心は本気モード)

The preliminaries continue as the next match pits Sand ninja Gaara's teammate Kankuro against Orochimaru's minion Misumi.
name: Kunoichi Rumble: The Rivals Get Serious!

description:
Japanese title: Besuto batoru wa shānnarō!! (ベストバトルはしゃーんなろー!!)

The fourth match is between Sakura and Ino, who are childhood friends and competitors for the affection of Sasuke.
name: The Ultimate Battle: Cha!

description:
Japanese title: Shikamaru tajitaji!? Kunoichi-tachi no atsuki tatakai (シカマルタジタジ!?くの一達の熱き戦い)

The fifth match is between Tenten and Temari. The sixth match is Shikamaru versus Kin.
name: Killer Kunoichi and a Shaky Shikamaru

description:
Japanese title: Akamaru sansen! Makeinu wa docchi da? (赤丸参戦!!負け犬はどっちだ?)

In the seventh match, Naruto clashes against Kiba, who brings along his dog Akamaru.
name: Akamaru Unleashed! Who's Top Dog Now?

description: We finally learn the true source of the Titans' goofy humor: pizza!
name: Truth, Justice, and What?

description:
Japanese title: Hinata sekimen! Kankyaku anguri, Naruto no oku no te (ヒナタ赤面! 観客あんぐり, ナルトの奥の手)

By consuming Food Pills, Kiba and Akamaru increase their chakra levels and start their counterattack on Naruto.
name: Surprise Attack! Naruto's Secret Weapon!

description: The Park Guys want to keep the park open for business.
name: Men In Uniform

description:
Japanese title: Byakugan kaigen!! Uchiki na Hinata no daitan ketsui! (白眼開眼!!内気なヒナタの大胆決意!)

Cousins Hinata and Neji of the Hyuga clan confront each other in the eighth match.
name: Byakugan Battle: Hinata Grows Bold!

description:
Japanese title: Akogare no hito no me no mae de!! (憧れの人の目の前で!!)

Hinata goes up against Neji, but he hits her pressure point by using his Byakugan (white eyes). Hinata's flow of chakra is stopped, and she almost loses consciousness.
name: A Failure Stands Tall!

description:
Japanese title: Gaara funsai!! Wakasa da! Pawā da! Bakuhatsu da! (我愛羅粉砕!!若さだ!パワーだ!爆発だ!)

Gaara finally appears in the ninth match, and his opponent is taijutsu (physical technique) specialist Lee.
name: Gaara Vs. Rock Lee: The Power of Youth Explodes!

description:
Japanese title: Nekketsu ochikobore! Tsuini Sakuretsu, kindan no ōgi! (熱血落ちこぼれ!遂に炸裂, 禁断の奥義!)

Lee uses the banned technique Primary Lotus to attack Gaara.
name: Lee's Hidden Strength: Forbidden Secret Jutsu!

description:
Japanese title: Aa Rokku Rī! Kore ga otoko no ikizama yo!! (嗚呼ロック·リー!これが男の生き様よ!!)

Lee decides to use the forbidden move, Hidden Lotus, as a last resort.
name: The Fifth Gate: A Splendid Ninja is Born

description:
Japanese title: Yami ni ugomeku kage Sasuke ni semaru kiki! (闇にうごめく影 サスケに迫る危機!)

In the final match of the preliminaries, Choji fights against Orochimaru's minion Dosu. The preliminaries are finally over, and the Hokage reveals the third exam.
name: A Shadow in Darkness: Danger Approaches Sasuke

description:
Japanese title: Ebisu futatabi! Harenchi wa watashi ga yurushimasen zo! (エビス再び!ハレンチは私が許しませんぞ!)

In preparation for the third exam that starts in a month, Naruto's former mentor, Kakashi, chooses Ebisu to train the young ninja.
name: Ebisu Returns: Naruto's Toughest Training Yet!

description:
Japanese title: Aiyashibaraku! Ero-sennin tōjō! (あいやしばらく!エロ仙人登場!)

Jiraiya, one of the legendary Three Ninja, suddenly appears before Ebisu and Naruto. Naruto gives Jiraiya the nickname, "Pervy Sage."
name: Long Time No See: Jiraiya Returns!

description:
Japanese title: Ero-sennin jikiden Kuchiyose no Jutsu dattebayo!! (エロ仙人直伝 口寄せの術だってばよ!!)

The Sound Ninja Dosu appears before Gaara and intends on defeating Gaara. But Gaara beats him soundly. Stealthily watching them are a Jonin of the Sand Village and Kabuto!
name: The Summoning Jutsu: Wisdom of the Toad Sage!

description:
Japanese title: Setsunai omoi Negai o kometa ichirin (切ない想い 願いを込めた一輪)

Naruto continues training under Jiraiya to master the "Summoning Jutsu" which enables him to call forth various living beasts. But he has a hard time controlling the Chakra of the Nine-Tailed Fox...
name: A Feeling of Yearning, A Flower Full of Hope

description:
Japanese title: Sei ka shi ka!? Menkyokaiden wa inochigake! (生か死か!?免許皆伝は命懸け!)

It is three weeks since Naruto began training under Jiraiya. And Naruto has been on the brink of collapse many times.
name: Live or Die: Risk it All to Win it All!

description:
Japanese title: Tonda! Haneta! Mogutta! Gama oyabun tōjō!! (飛んだ!跳ねた!潜った!ガマ親分登場!!)

Naruto is finally able to draw out the Nine-Tail Chakra and utilize the "Summoning Jutsu." Gamabunta appears and does not believe that Naruto summoned him.
name: He Flies! He Jumps! He Lurks! Chief Toad Appears!

description:
Japanese title: Shinobiyoru ma no te! Nerawareta Byōshitsu (しのび寄る魔の手!狙われた病室)

On the day of the test, Gaara disappears from the inn where the Sand Ninja are staying and goes to Hidden Leaf Hospital.
name: Hospital Besieged: The Evil Hand Revealed!

description:
Japanese title: Mō retsu Mō Tsui Mō Dasshu Hansen kaishi dattebayo (モー烈 モー追 モーダッシュ 本選開始だってばよ)

The day of the Exam finally arrives. Naruto’s first opponent is Neji Hyuga.
name: The Final Rounds: Rush to the Battle Arena!

description:
Japanese title: Byakugan bāsasu Kage Bunshin! Ore wa zettē katsu!! (白眼VS影分身!オレはゼってー勝つ!!)

Finally, Chunin Exam starts with the eight Ninja who qualified in the preliminaries. But Sasuke is nowhere to be found.
name: Byakugan Vs. Shadow Clone Jutsu!

description:
Japanese title: Shikaku zero! Mō hitotsu no zettai bōgyo (死角ゼロ!もうひとつの絶対防御)

Naruto is unable to use his Shadow Clone Jutsu against Neji who can see chakra points!
name: Ultimate Defense: Zero Blind Spot!

description:
Japanese title: Ochikobore no Sokojikara! (落ちこぼれの底力!)

Naruto and Neji’s battle continue with Neji showing enormous power.
name: A Failure's True Power

description:
Japanese title: Shikkaku!? Kiken! Maedaoshi! Haranbukumi no daihonsen! (失格!?キケン!前倒し!波乱含みの大本戦)

Defeated by Naruto, Neji is being taken to the hospital, when Neji’s uncle Hiashi appears.
name: Hit it or Quit it: The Final Rounds Get Complicated!

description:
Japanese title: Kumo wa ii naa... yaruki zero no otoko (雲はいいなあ...やる気ゼロの男)

Sasuke’s match is postponed and suddenly, it is Shikamaru’s turn. He has shown no eagerness to fight, thinking that his is merely a secondary match…
name: Zero Motivation: The Guy with Cloud Envy!

description:
Japanese title: Gekitotsu! Konoha mai Suna ugomeku toki (激突!木ノ葉舞い砂うごめく瞬間)

In the Shikamaru and Temari’s match, Shikamaru who had the upper hand suddenly makes a surprising decision!
name: Dancing Leaf, Squirming Sand

description:
Japanese title: Arashi o yobu otoko!! Sasuke no Gejimayu-ryū Taijutsu! (嵐を呼ぶ男!!サスケのゲジマユ流体術!)

Sasuke and Gaara’a anticipated match begins. Gaara eerily talks to himself, as though addressing someone.
name: Bushy Brow’s Jutsu: Sasuke Style!

description:
Japanese title: Date ni okureta wake ja nai! Kyūkyoku ōgi - Chidori tanjō!! (だてに遅れたわけじゃない!究極奥義·千鳥誕生!!)

Sauske's speed and moves are identical to Lee’s Taijutsu. But Gaara is not an opponent who can be defeated with just Taijutsu.
name: Late for the Show, But Ready to Go! The Ultimate Secret Technique is Born!

description:
Japanese title: Konoha Kuzushi" Shidō! (「木ノ葉崩し」始動!)

During the match, someone has used Genjutsu to put everyone in the arena to sleep. The Sand Ninja led by Orochimaru have begun their plan to destroy the Hidden Leaf Village.
name: Zero Hour! The Destruction of the Hidden Leaf Village Begins!

description:
Japanese title: Mattemashita! Ē-ranku ninmu dattebayo!! (待ってました!Aランク任務だってばよ!!)

The Sound and Sand Ninja, along with Orochimaru, begin their move to destroy Hidden Leaf Village. The arena has become a battleground.
name: Village in Distress: A New A-Ranked Mission!

description:
Japanese title: Nigegoshi nanbaa wan Mendokuse~ ga yarukkya nē!! (逃げ腰NO.1 めんどくせーがやろっきゃねえ!!)

Along with Pakkun, Naruto, Sakura and Shikamaru are in hot pursuit of Sasuke. Pakkun senses nine of Orochimaru's men coming after them.
name: A Shirker’s Call to Action: Layabout No More!

description:
Japanese title: Kokon musō! "Hokage" to iu reberu no tatakai (古今無双!「火影」というレベルの戦い)

Orochimaru traps the Hokage inside a barrier and continue to battle.
name: An Unrivaled Match: Hokage Battle Royale!

description:
Japanese title: Hokage no ayamachi Kamen ni shita no sugao (火影の過ち 仮面の下の素顔)

Sasuke finally catches up to Gaara, Temari, and Kankuro. Kankuro escapes with Gaara leaving Temari to face Sasuke.
name: A Mistake from the Past: A Face Revealed!

description: Note: Rio only appears in a music sequence.
name: In Search of the Stolen Album

description:
Japanese title: Kinjutsu ōgi! "Shiki Fūjin" (禁術奥義!「屍鬼封尽」)

The battle between the Hokage and Orochimaru rages on. Finally, the Hokage resorts to a Jutsu unknown to Orochimaru, the Sealing Jutsu known as “Reaper Death Seal.”
name: Forbidden Secret Technique: Reaper Death Seal!

description:
Japanese title: Kyōgaku! Gaara no Shōtai (驚愕!我愛羅の正体)

Shino appears as Sasuke and Kankuro battle. Leaving Shino to handle Kankuro, Sasuke goes after Gaara.
name: Astonishing Truth! Gaara’s Identity Emerges!

description:
Japanese title: Genkai o koete... Sasuke no ketsudan!! (限界を越えて... サスケの決断!!)

Half of Gaara’s body has transformed and Sasuke continues his battle against him.
name: Sasuke’s Decision: Pushed to the Edge!

description:
Japanese title: Tsukiyo no ansatsusha (月夜の暗殺者)

By the time Naruto and Sakura catch up, Sasuke has exhausted his strength and collapsed.
name: Assassin of the Moonlit Night

description: A sociopathic scientist drags his innocent grandson on dangerous inter-dimensional adventures.
name: Pilot

description: Rick helps Jerry out with the dog, broh. Don't even trip about this episode, because they also incept Goldenfold. (Guest starring Rob Paulsen and Jess Harnell)
name: Lawnmower Dog

description: It's Christmas. Rick shrinks Morty, injecting him into a homeless man to save Anatomy Park. Jerry tries to have a Christmas free of electronic devices, but regrets his decision when his parents introduce him to their new friend.
name: Anatomy Park

description: Rick and Morty try to get to the bottom of a mystery in this M. Night Shamyaloin style twistaroony of an episode! (Guest Starring David Cross)
name: M. Night Shaym-Aliens!

description: Rick provides the family with a solution to their problems, freeing him up to go on an adventure led by Morty. Sounds good, better record this one, broh!
name: Meeseeks and Destroy

description: Rick provides Morty with a love potion to get Jessica. The serum backfires & Rick's attempt to fix things creates Cronenberg inspired monsters. Rick is okay with it but Morty feels partly responsible for creating a living nightmare.
name: Rick Potion #9

description: Morty convinces Rick to buy him a sexy robot. Guess what tho? Trouble happens, dog. (Guest starring Claudia Black and Richard Christy)
name: Raising Gazorpazorp

description: When Rick hooks up the family's tv receiver with reality-tv shows from alternate dimensions, and allows them to see themselves in different versions of their lives, they begin to wonder what they have, and more importantly - what could have been.
name: Rixty Minutes

description: Rick goes to battle with the devil, and Summer gets upset about it, broh. Plus Jerry and Morty hang out, broh! (Guest starring Alfred Molina, Nolan North, and Rich Fulcher)
name: Something Ricked This Way Comes

description: Beth and Jerry head for an iceberg of a date leaving Rick in charge. Morty doesn't get to go on any more adventures if the house isn't in the same condition when they get back.
name: Ricksy Business

description:
Japanese title: Hikari to Yami Gaara to iu na (光と闇 我愛羅という名)

Naruto is helpless against Gara’s immense power. While Naruto declares that he fights for his comrades, Gaara says he fights for himself.
name: Light Vs. Dark: The Two Faces of Gaara

description: Rick has a run in with some old associates, resulting in a fallout with Morty. You got any chips, broh?
name: Close Rick-counters of the Rick Kind

description:
Japanese title: Bakuhatsu! Kore zo Naruto ninpōchō~~!! (爆発!これぞナルト忍法帖〜〜っ!!)

Naruto is helpless against Gaara’s overpowering strength. However, after seeing Sasuke risking life and limb to save him and Sakura…
name: Naruto’s Ninja Handbook

description:
Japanese title: Rimitto bucchigiri! ~Hikari to Yami~ (リミットぶっちぎり! 〜光と闇〜)

Gaara employs his Playing Possum Jutsu, which allows the Sand Spirit within him, Shukaku, to display its true power.
name: Beyond the Limit of Darkness and Light

description:
Japanese title: Sandaime yo, towa ni......!! (三代目よ, 永久に......!!)

With every ounce of their power, Gaara and Naruto continue to fight. Determined to protect Sakura, Naruto attacks Gaara again and again.
name: The Third Hokage, Forever...

description:
Japanese title: Asagiri no kikyō (朝霧の帰郷)

Orochimaru's plan to destroy the Village Hidden in the Leaves is stopped. But the damage is extensive and work proceeds quickly to make repairs.
name: Return of the Morning Mist

description:
Japanese title: Sharingan tai Sharingan!! (写輪眼VS写輪眼!!)

Kakashi arrives in the nick of time to help Asuma and Kurenai, and Itachi too enters the fray. The ultimate battle between two Sharingan users begins.
name: Eye to Eye: Sharingan Vs. Sharingan!

description:
Japanese title: Ō, nō~! Jiraiya no jonan, Naruto no sainan (おお, のォ〜っ!自来也の女難, ナルトの災難)

Jiraiya and Naruto are on a journey to find Tsunade, one of the legendary Sannin. Jiraiya's purpose is both to protect Naruto from the clutches of the mysterious organization the Akatsuki and to train his apprentice.
name: Jiraiya: Naruto's Potential Disaster!

description: DONNA SMOAK RETURNS — During an attack on the mayor’s office, Ray (Brandon Routh) is critically injured. Felicity (Emily Bett Rickards) is pleasantly surprised when her mother, Donna Smoak (guest star Charlotte Ross), shows up at the hospital to offer her support. With the SCPD out in full force looking for the assailant, Oliver (Stephen Amell) and his team work hard to stay one step ahead of the police to find the man responsible. However, things come to a head when Ra’s al Ghul (guest star Matt Nable) kidnaps Captain Lance (Paul Blackthorne).
name: Public Enemy
There's No Creature Like Snow Creature
Big Scare in the Big Easy
It's Mean, It's Green, It's the Mystery Machine
